This paper involves computer vision techniques for 3D reconstruction and style transfer, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper deals with graphics and animation, which could place it in the Graphics (cs.GR) or Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The use of a VAE-CycleGAN also suggests that the paper could belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
